metadata.name: Blue Bliss #1/20
metadata.description:
Blue Bliss is a special edition to celebrate my birthday on 12/20/2022.  
It's my thank you gift to my collectors and to the closest friends I've made in my first year in the NFT world. 
Each one of you is special to me in a unique way, thank you with all my love!
